			<slide id="product-challenges">
				<title>Challenges for API Products</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>Productization:</em> APIs must be useful, findable, usable, and predictable</li>
					<li><em>Adoption:</em> API design familiarity allows for easier adoption</li>
					<li><em>Velocity:</em> Improving an API allows to grow the value rate</li>
					<li><em>Breaking changes:</em> Breaking changes fragment the consumer population</li>
				</ul>
