			<slide id="landscape-lifecycle">
				<title>Lifecycle Management at Landscape Level</title>
				<ul>
					<li><em>API Lifecycle Management</em> helps with improving API value</li>
					<li><em>API Governance</em> helps with improving API landscape value</li>
					<li>Focus on improving UX at the API landscape level</li>
					<ul>
						<li>UX can be improved by good API DX</li>
						<li>UX can be improved by good API landscape DX</li>
					</ul>
				</ul>
